'''DistroWatch'''是一個包含了各種[[Linux发行版|Linux发行版]]及其他[[自由软件|自由]]/[[开放源代码|开放源代码]]的[[类Unix系统|類Unix]][[操作系统|操作系统]]（如[[OpenSolaris|OpenSolaris]]、[[MINIX|MINIX]]及[[BSD|BSD]]等）的新聞、人氣排名、以及其他一般資訊等的[[網站|網站]]。它包含了數百種發行版的資訊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://distrowatch.com/search.php?status=All|title=DistroWatch.com: Put the fun back into computing. Use Linux, BSD.|work=DistroWatch|accessdate=8 July 2012|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327101125/https://distrowatch.com/search.php?status=All|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它最初在2001年5月31日發佈，並由Ladislav Bodnar維護<ref>{{cite web|url=http://distrowatch.com/dwres.php?resource=about|title=DistroWatch.com: Put the fun back into computing. Use Linux, BSD.|work=DistroWatch|accessdate=8 July 2012|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521230506/https://distrowatch.com/dwres.php?resource=about|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

這個網頁包含了很多不同發行版的軟體套裝及版本的細節比較表。也包含了一些基本特徵如價格及支援的處理器架構等<ref>範例：見[[Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux|Red Hat Enterprise Linux]]的頁面 http://distrowatch.com/table.php?distribution=redhat {{Wayback|url=http://distrowatch.com/table.php?distribution=redhat |date=20140210042533 }}</ref>。其也有DistroWatch週刊（Distrowatch weekly，常縮寫為DWW），每週一出刊“細數一週來在發行版世界發生的所有大小事”<ref name=weekly_20081117>{{cite web|url=http://distrowatch.com/weekly.php?issue=20081117|title=DistroWatch.com: Put the fun back into computing. Use Linux, BSD.|work=DistroWatch|accessdate=8 July 2012|archive-date=2014-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131095728/http://distrowatch.com/weekly.php?issue=20081117|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。{{As of|2008|11|17}}，5年半，278期後，Ladislav決定卸下DWW編輯的位置。Ladislav表示他將會繼續“釋出最新的新聞並保持所有發行版頁面為最新的狀態”<ref name=weekly_20081117/>，而DWW將會由Chris Smart接手編寫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://distrowatch.com/weekly.php?issue=20081124|title=DistroWatch.com: Put the fun back into computing. Use Linux, BSD.|work=DistroWatch|accessdate=8 July 2012|archive-date=2014-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131095712/http://distrowatch.com/weekly.php?issue=20081124|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Distrowatch有一個每月捐助計畫，DistroWatch及兩個線上商店販賣低成本的Linux、BSD及其他開放原始碼軟體的CD及DVD。{{As of|2010|06|07}}，DistroWatch總共捐出了24,478美元給許多不同的開放原始碼軟體專案（自2004年3月起）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://distrowatch.com/weekly.php?issue=20100607|title=DistroWatch.com: Put the fun back into computing. Use Linux, BSD.|work=DistroWatch|accessdate=8 July 2012|archive-date=2014-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131092518/http://distrowatch.com/weekly.php?issue=20100607|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 準確性 ==

=== 點擊計數器的準確度 ===

Bodnar寫道“我相信那些統計數字還是有點真實性的，但老實說，它們真的並不代表一切，不應該太認真的對待”及“並不是市場佔有率或品質的指標...”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.groklaw.net/articlebasic.php?story=20070111043418436|title=Groklaw - Some Facts about openSUSE and Distrowatch Figures - A Correction|publisher=Groklaw|accessdate=17 June 2012|date=11 January 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120519140817/http://www.groklaw.net/articlebasic.php?story=20070111043418436|archive-date=2012-05-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[PC_World|PCWorld]]寫道“DistroWatch的頁面點擊數的確是部份發行版感興趣的東西，但不能以此代表真正使用或整體偏好的狀況”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/254516/which_linux_distro_is_fairest_of_them_all_ubuntu_survey_says.html|title=Which Linux Distro Is Fairest of Them All? Ubuntu, Survey Says|publisher=PCWorld|date=25 April 2012|accessdate=17 June 2012|first=Katherine|last=Noyes|archive-date=2012-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814141728/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/254516/which_linux_distro_is_fairest_of_them_all_ubuntu_survey_says.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Muktware寫道“DistroWatch並不是‘有多少使用者’的指標，但的確可以用來觀查使用者正在找什麼”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.muktware.com/3193/linux-mint-touches-all-time-high-distrowatch-will-ubuntu-recover|title=Linux Mint Touches All Time High On DistroWatch, Will Ubuntu Recover?|first=Neil|last=Richards|date=10 January 2012Z|accessdate=8 July 2012|work=Muktware|archive-date=2013-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221042345/http://www.muktware.com/3193/linux-mint-touches-all-time-high-distrowatch-will-ubuntu-recover|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

